Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.26,Default,title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(984,0)\1c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H00FFFF&\pos(449,343)}{\fs26}Otani's Catastrophic Declaration!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.84,0:01:45.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobu-chan received her acceptance notice from the undergraduate university in Hokkaido,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.60,0:01:48.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,and she's been even more lovey-dovey with Nakao-chi than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:53.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani, who wants to become a teacher, has started attending prep classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.19,0:01:57.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,and is studying seriously for the entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:02:02.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like studying or taking tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.36,0:02:05.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've given up on the idea of going to university and decided to try for a technical college instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.95,0:02:08.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:09.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:12.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do about the next Umibouzu Concert?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna pass this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Umibouzu we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.63,0:02:22.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last Umibouzu concert of the year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:25.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! But I don't really have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:27.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the only time I have to study for exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.39,0:02:29.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was choking back tears when I finally decided not to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.89,0:02:33.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.39,0:02:36.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Who was it who said she was going to support me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.15,0:02:38.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Examinees sure have it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.32,0:02:40.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mocking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.19,0:02:41.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.40,0:02:46.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If not, stop talking to me while I'm trying to memorize English vocab. Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Otani.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.45,0:02:49.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet. Why are you following me anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.29,0:02:53.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to put it like that. I've got a reason for coming this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? A reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.42,0:02:57.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My part-time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.42,0:02:59.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's at the restaurant opposite your prep school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.75,0:03:02.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you working all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:05.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This way I can at least walk you halfway home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.73,0:03:17.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ribbon isn't on straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.61,0:03:19.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.65,0:03:22.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And your nails are too long. Please cut them before you come tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:25.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And tie your hair up tighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.70,0:03:26.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:28.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.99,0:03:29.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kohori-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:31.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That gave me a start!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're five minutes late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.50,0:03:40.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is the second day in a row.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.96,0:03:43.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was held back at school by my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:47.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you to call ahead if that happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.59,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Another part-timer? What a cute boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.26,0:03:54.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,An Umibouzu wristband!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.10,0:03:56.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's the limited edition one that you can only get at his concerts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:57.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.39,0:03:59.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're a huge Umibouzu fan too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:01.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,A mega fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:02.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:06.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's awesome to have another Umibouzu fan around!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.15,0:04:09.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! I'm feeling all excited now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:12.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san! Kohori-kun! Stop that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.91,0:04:16.66,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...{overlap}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:23.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,These dumplings are just delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.55,0:04:24.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:24.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.05,0:04:28.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. You made them, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:32.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So what's this younger kitchen-hand co-worker of yours like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.26,0:04:33.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Konori-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.89,0:04:37.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,His face is kind of cute, and he's about as tall as Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:40.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is your midget fetish speaking to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:41.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's got a midget fetish?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.98,0:04:45.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Otani-kun seems to be working really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.40,0:04:48.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Otani-kun is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:54.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard he stayed back late yesterday, and was asking the teacher lots of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.74,0:04:56.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,is that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:05:00.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani really is trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oooooh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:07.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.92,0:05:08.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.97,0:05:10.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:15.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I said: if I put my mind to it, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:16.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.68,0:05:20.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, getting into college won't be impossible for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:23.10,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,In comparison, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.69,0:05:26.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to decide what I'm going to do with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.94,0:05:29.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should just start doing this full time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:32.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.87,0:05:33.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:34.87,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorr-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Owww!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.79,0:05:38.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:41.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Man... I really can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.42,alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't always make so much of a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was thinking of doing this full time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.63,0:05:45.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:07.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it needs more salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:08.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too sweet, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don t get this part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.78,0:06:13.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Use this formula...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:18.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's up with all of you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.95,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're all ready to fly off into the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Risa, you're here? Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:28.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should add yams to the recipe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:29.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, you're a genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:31.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll definitely become a great artisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow... somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:40.39,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm being left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.28,0:07:00.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,My face looks terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.20,0:07:03.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get yelled at again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:05.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.54,0:07:09.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.26,0:07:13.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She said "Welcome."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:14.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying, "What did you come here for" to your customers? How rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:18.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Did you come just to laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.18,0:07:24.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me. This waitress's attitude is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:30.77,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me know what you would like to order.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:33.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:34.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.19,0:07:35.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,At least let me finish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:37.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,P-P-P-P-P-P-Please go ahead...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that hurt, you idiot! I'm a customer, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.62,0:07:42.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:43.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to prep class in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.50,0:07:45.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:47.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,They even hold them on Sundays?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.62,0:07:49.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no weekends for examinees.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.38,0:07:51.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially not for the ones with bad grades.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.05,0:07:51.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly, exact-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:52.80,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Enough, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:56.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Say Risa, where's that cute kitchen-hand you mentioned last time? Not working today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:08:00.30,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kohori-kun? Doesn't look like he's here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.51,0:08:01.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.93,0:08:04.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Midget fetishist Risa's next target.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.85,0:08:05.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Midget fetishist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What? So that guy is short too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:13.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That s not important!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:15.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a huge Umibouzu fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.61,0:08:17.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get yelled at if I keep talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:21.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, my order...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:33.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well... She seems a lot happier than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.42,0:08:35.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:39.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You said you came to laugh at her, but you were actually worried about her, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:43.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she was down about continually getting chewed out before.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.31,0:08:43.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:44.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.68,0:08:45.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.85,0:08:47.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:49.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that, you idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.60,0:08:52.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,An examinee's got no time to worry about others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.44,0:08:53.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:56.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're like that, Risa will hook up with that cute short kid behind your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.99,0:08:58.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.74,0:08:59.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don t be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:04.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Otani has class on Sundays too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:07.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your patronage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.08,0:09:10.12,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.29,0:09:11.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya, Risa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.25,0:09:18.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to go out with him next Sunday since I'll have the day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.13,0:09:21.63,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. He's an examinee; it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.19,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz270.451\c&H1E1519&\3c&H797575&\fscx246.25\fscy188.75\pos(633,218)}Gloom
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:32.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this odd, gloomy atmosphere?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:33.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:36.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, idiot. Don't talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.74,0:09:39.73,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Risa, over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.24,0:09:43.49,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We heard he did terribly in the practice exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:46.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The results for his top choice school were all C's.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:48.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.24,0:09:49.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:51.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.25,0:09:56.84,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I even sacrificed sleep for study...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:57.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:02.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, even if you start studying now, you can't expect your grades to go up right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.05,0:10:05.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got time, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:07.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy for you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:09.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.06,0:10:11.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll wear yourself out at this rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... You're just crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:17.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This has nothing to do with anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.92,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop blurting out whatever comes into your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Do what you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.11,0:10:25.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've done that without you telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:34.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:37.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that all about?\N Am I getting in his way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:41.46,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I know he's under a lot of stress, but couldn't he have been a little nicer?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:43.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi- san!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Kohori-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:48.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! We're on together again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:54.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.56,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. I cut myself just now when I was sharpening the knives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:10:59.52,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what to do about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:07.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.83,0:11:12.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:17.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I break glasses and cut my hands all the time, so I've had to use the first aid kit a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.04,0:11:21.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Old lady Matsumara helped me at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:24.13,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,but I kept getting hurt, so she told me I should deal with it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.13,0:11:26.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll get angry if she hears you calling her an old lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.80,0:11:29.22,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! She's not here, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty funny, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.81,0:11:37.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really funny and kind. You re a great person.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.45,0:11:40.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:41.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.65,0:11:46.32,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working here for six months, but this is the first time I've met someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:46.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.49,0:11:50.03,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in the kitchen, you're famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.03,0:11:51.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,We can always hear you shouting from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like "Whoops!" or" I'm so sorry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:55.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.00,0:11:59.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I get yelled at by old lady Matsumara for shouting loudly like that too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:00.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. I called her "old lady" again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:04.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Man! She's definitely not around, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You re so funny! My stomach hurts from laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm feeling better now, at any rate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:25.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather forecast was correct. I was right to bring my umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.12,0:12:32.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You've still got time, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This way I can at least walk you halfway home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:41.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She... probably didn't bring an umbrella.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:54.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsumara- san, is everything on our menu is available for take-out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:55.35,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:12:59.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you don't memorize the entire menu tonight, I'm not letting you go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.65,0:13:03.44,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there sure is a lot of text. I'm getting sleepy just looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You make mistakes because you don't know the menu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.65,0:13:08.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I've memorized all of the noodle meals perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.65,0:13:11.53,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you have. We only have two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:18.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. So all of these menu items can also be take-out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.17,0:13:25.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should get something for Otani to have for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:28.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.88,0:13:30.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:34.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped~ Can't be helped~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.72,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be helped~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.14,0:13:36.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.48,0:13:49.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san? Why are you sleeping here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:50.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.24,0:13:52.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.37,0:13:54.57,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:31.11,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,If I bring him dinner, Otani will probably be surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.71,0:14:42.29,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:45.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.83,0:14:50.31,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That was, uhhh... S-S-S-{this and next line are alpha timed}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.31,0:14:51.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That was, uhhh... S-S-S-S-S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:59.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I w-wasn't... th-that... uh... th-this... I wasn't kissing you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.66,0:15:24.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.96,0:15:27.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think, Otani. Please listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:30.38,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was who Nobu-chan was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:34.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Midget fetishist!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.89,0:15:42.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:56.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm studying. Please be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.37,0:15:58.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:58.70,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She cheated on me with that midget she works with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:02.45,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.62,0:16:03.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, you got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:04.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How am I wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:07.54,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it clearly. He definitely kissed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.83,0:16:08.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.25,0:16:10.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:11.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So you only wanted me for my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.76,0:16:15.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.93,0:16:18.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So it doesn't matter who it is, as long as they're short? You pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.68,0:16:19.89,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:23.85,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would deliberately look for a boyfriend shorter than them? Thats so uncool!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:26.81,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Uncool? You're calling me uncool?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.37,0:16:28.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:32.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how busy Otani is with his exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:33.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you would two-time him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:35.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.07,0:16:37.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were like that, Risa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.74,0:16:38.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.82,0:16:39.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.37,0:16:40.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you just listen to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.58,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:49.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, there's absolutely nothing going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.71,0:16:52.25,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You might say there isn't, but he went and did something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.25,0:16:53.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows what he thinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.84,0:16:56.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, even if you ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:58.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:16:58.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:16:59.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.18,0:17:05.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'd already finished work... and if I'd stayed to chat, I would've been yelled at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.18,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:12.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Honestly, I'm not two-timing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.07,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I believe you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:17.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.74,0:17:19.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Then tell that shorty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.32,0:17:19.82,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:22.74,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time he tries to lay a hand on you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.74,0:17:25.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give him a hook so hard his nose will be crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.20,0:17:28.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you shouldn't punch him in the nose...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.37,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious. I'll really do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:34.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've hit him when I had the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:39.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Seeing him this upset over me makes me kind of happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:42.47,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:51.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about yesterday! It was a moment of weakness, and by the time I realized...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:53.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.36,0:17:58.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That was your boyfriend, right? I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.11,0:18:00.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kohori-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:03.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no big deal. Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.70,0:18:06.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.54,0:18:11.33,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Not really. I was asleep anyway, so I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:13.04,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.75,0:18:14.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.67,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.63,0:18:19.05,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you busy this Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:19.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.42,0:18:22.51,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an Umibouzu event.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:25.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Umibouzu... Umibouzu... Umibouzu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.60,0:18:28.60,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? What kind of event?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:32.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a radio event. Only fifty people get to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! And you won?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! And I'd like to invite you. Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.65,0:18:40.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.24,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really like to go with you, Koizumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.91,0:18:46.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't do anything that will make trouble for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.79,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to come?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.58,0:18:51.91,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:19:00.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go? Taking everything into consideration, it's obvious that I shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:07.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I'm not interested in him, going to a concert with him after what happened is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.18,0:19:10.68,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no excuse this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:13.64,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.10,0:19:15.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:17.69,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! No way! No way! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.86,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So... it s a "no," then?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.62,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:32.20,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.96,0:19:34.41,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:35.96,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, yay, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.96,0:19:39.59,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the world's biggest idiot!\N I couldn't say no to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:45.55,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not cheating. \NWe're just going to a concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.97,0:19:49.01,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hurry there and then hurry on home once it's finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:51.93,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.44,0:19:58.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.52,0:20:01.15,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,See you again at Osaka Castle Hall next year!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.15,0:20:02.36,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:06.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. That ends our broadcast of the Umibouzu concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.99,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,She was at work so she'll definitely be happy when I give this to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.99,0:20:14.16,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It was an invite-only concert, after all - a once in a lifetime thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:16.50,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:19.17,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my first time seeing Umibouzu perform before such a small audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:20.09,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:23.34,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for inviting me to such a great event.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.26,0:20:29.43,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I finally invited you out. I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:30.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:34.98,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.27,0:20:40.90,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.17,0:20:47.28,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually... I... towards you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.83,0:21:00.08,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:01.21,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:02.42,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.67,0:21:05.71,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:09.76,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't laugh! I'm asking you what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.48,0:21:17.48,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.23,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who pressured her into going to the Umibouzu concert with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:22.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Koizumi-san didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.65,0:21:23.61,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Kohori-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:24.94,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.65,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,So the two of you went to a concert together?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.99,0:21:30.66,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that. I was the one who really wanted to go to the concert.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.12,0:21:34.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who's in the wrong, so if you really want to break someone's nose, break mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.17,0:21:40.00,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.17,0:21:41.75,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. I don't care anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.84,0:21:44.88,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.80,0:21:47.26,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm breaking up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:49.97,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't go out with someone like you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.89,0:22:00.14,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,,Otani...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.65,0:23:27.19,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,, Don't say you're going to break up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.19,0:23:29.02,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,, Do what you want with that midget, Koizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:30.78,lovely,,0000,0000,0000,, What do you mean, "midget"? He's taller than you.
